release_note: Fixed minor bugs and made improvements.
We developed a survey functionality in this version.
Added the daily streak feature and the ability to select from 4 voices in non English languages.
Fixed bugs related to 5 free daily messages
Made major improvements and fixed bugs
Fixed bugs
Fixed bugs added a basic lessons curriculum and introduced an onboarding helper.
Developed hands free mode
Fixed bugs and upgraded chat settings.
Fixed bugs.
We have developed a new grammar lesson and quiz based on saved grammar feedback. Additionally we have improved our chat experience.
We have improved the speech detection model.
We added a feature that lets you take a vocabulary quiz with bookmarked words.
You can now view feedback on your fluency during a lesson and compare your pronunciation with a native speaker s.
You can now save grammar feedback expressions and feedback by tapping the bookmark button after finishing a lesson.
You can now choose AI speaker s voice before starting a lesson. This feature is only available when you are learning English.
Fixed bugs and made improvements.

You can now translate from your native language to the language you are learning. We also built a feature that lets you send us feedback in chat so please feel free to share any suggestions or report bugs!
You can now tap a word in chat to see its definition.
Check out AI tutors feedback on your grammar and fluency after a lesson ends!
The design of the home and speaking interaction have been completely upgraded!
You can now check your lesson s progress and earn a badge once you finish a lesson. On your profile page check out the stats related to your study so you can stay motivated!
You can now save chats and type messages.
Learners can now set the difficulty level from basic to advanced and the conversations will be adjusted accordingly.
